'''

Looping types

		1. Selective -- only one will get executed at time out of
						multiple conditions
					if..else  -- if we have limitied 2-3 conditions then you shud go for if else
							if..else -- every condition will be checked and satified will be executed
									this is time consuming task -- will affect application performnace
							
					switch  -- 
						Multiple if.else conditions should be replaced by Switch conditions
						Jump ---
					
		2. Transfer
					-- break -- Exit the current loop
		
			-- continue -- skip the current iteration
					
					tya interation madhe tyacha khalcha code  execute hot nah
					
					
		3. Iterative
					-- for loop -- if you are aware about the interations
					--while -- if you dont know the no
							of iterations in advance then should	
							go for while loop
		
		
		
		
		
		
		
		


